<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.221">德義在人者<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.222">兮何而德加<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.223">有殆德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.224">王若知<lb/></seg>
