<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.226">文子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.227">「臣聞傳曰致功之道<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.228">地之守也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.229">故王者以天地為功<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.230">□□善，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.231">致其功□□□功，<lb/></seg>
