<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.234">故功成名遂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.235">與天地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.236">欸窅∥窅以致<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.237">□曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.238">王知者先，<lb/></seg>
