<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.249">平王<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.250">□不化為之奈何？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.251">文子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.252">「不□人<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.253">反本教約而國富，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.254">故聖<lb/></seg>
