<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.317">聞忠而陳其所□言<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.318">而民<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.319">毋維，<lb/></seg>
