<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.321">□，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.322">而民毋病，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.323">毋好味<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.324">□親隨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.325">是以國家之昌而功名<lb/></seg>
