<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.335">百國之君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.336">皆驩然思欲愛<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.337">子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.338">「君子之驕奢不施，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4102_CHANT_010-1a.339">謂之無德<lb/></seg>
